6 日晚，涉事出租车驾驶员刘某燕，因候客时间较长，承接短途订单心生不满，在营运过程中对乘客发表不当言论，言语失当，服务态度恶劣，依据相关规定，做出顶格行政处罚的处理决定。目前，执法部门已对涉事驾驶员作出记扣 20 分，暂扣从业资格证及营运车辆，并对涉事出租车企业负责人进行约谈。 此前报道： 5 月 6 日晚，网民发布一段 4 分钟录音称「太原一出租车司机狂喷打车乘客」。该网民在贴文中称，「司机一听是大学生就开喷」。记者私信该网民，截至发稿未获回复。太原市交通局综合执法队称，收到舆情转办件，正按流程核查处理。 内容来源太原官方通报「出租车司机狂喷乘客」：顶格处罚 _ 录音 _ 营运 _ 驾驶员"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-2f6ea125efd7de5b35cd5497ec2485ae.png"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "107 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2036037033882286030"}}, "attached_info": "CkoI+7T32MO794gbEAMaCTExOTQyMzM1OCCgovXPBjAAON0GQAlyEzIwMzYwMzcwMzM4ODIyODYwMzB4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "10_1778363010.237776", "card_id": "Q_2036152296388523178", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 29}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么 ChatGPT 跟中文用户对话时，「我会稳稳地接住你」常会莫名其妙冒出来？你还发现 AI 的哪些怪癖？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "ChatGPT 跟中文用户对话，有一句话已经被吐槽了大半年：「我会稳稳地接住你」。不管是问数学题、让它写代码，还是要它生成图片，这句话都会莫名其妙冒出来。"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-ac1c997332dd6608269888e3b4bd9b3c_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "104 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2036152296388523178"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI+7T32MO794gbEAMaCTExOTQyOTkwNCD5+PbPBjAAOHBACnITMjAzNjE1MjI5NjM4ODUyMzE3OHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "11_1778363010.238122", "card_id": "Q_2036112283781293052", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b7